  "2402470": {
    "name": "World of Anterra",
    "steam_appid": 2402470,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402470/extras/9c13c1a6a57e37a542d9cda3b3d3be78.avif?t=1764363478\" width=920 height=214 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >World of Anterra is an epic non-linear, open-world role playing adventure. The game features a handcrafted open world, deep progression systems, fast paced combat, and rich lore, all wrapped in a satisfying and tactile interface. It’s the type of game only an independent studio could make!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402470/extras/531568fea36ca06c98d52a18d8d2277b.avif?t=1764363478\" width=920 height=653 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402470/extras/0ee53fca4b8e7c17f9e15103cf29dfe1.avif?t=1764363478\" width=1200 height=278 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402470/extras/a68863daeda39cd93ab1eb359c1d3ef1.poster.avif?t=1764363478\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402470/extras/a68863daeda39cd93ab1eb359c1d3ef1.webm?t=1764363478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402470/extras/a68863daeda39cd93ab1eb359c1d3ef1.mp4?t=1764363478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Combat may look like a typical party-based tactics game, but don't be fooled! It’s the most streamlined grid-based combat you've ever seen. It’s so simple, you can use a single button to blast through low-risk combat scenarios like an action game, but has the depth and strategy needed to overcome more challenging opponents and bosses.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402470/extras/023be86f0f1c46128d1de409819129b4.avif?t=1764363478\" width=1200 height=278 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402470/extras/49cc66a2963ea782ccf3760d974c9a3d.poster.avif?t=1764363478\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402470/extras/49cc66a2963ea782ccf3760d974c9a3d.webm?t=1764363478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402470/extras/49cc66a2963ea782ccf3760d974c9a3d.mp4?t=1764363478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >A mysterious eye watches over the realms as the throne sits empty. You are the prophesized, the traveller from another world, but why are you here? Is it to save Anterra? … or yourself?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >World of Anterra tells a sweeping story with twists and turns that pull inspiration from current and historical events, science, and philosophy. Don’t expect walls of text though. You will uncover the story and the world’s lore through your conversations, experiences and discoveries. The narrative unfolds naturally, based on the paths you choose to follow. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dialogue is snappy and feels natural. It allows you to have authentic interactions with every character in the game, with the least amount of text. The design is heavily inspired by retro RPGs like Ultima, but modernized to meet the expectations of a contemporary player. You will uncover secrets and lore about the world in a way that most games fail to do.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402470/extras/a56fc958dfabfcd2778e7629a3705c47.avif?t=1764363478\" width=1200 height=278 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402470/extras/Steam_-_Map_Scale_4.GIF?t=1764363478\" /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Explore the massive and sprawling world of Anterra. Find hidden locations, dynamic scenarios and new mysteries to solve as you forge your own unique journey.</p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Spot areas of interest from the overworld.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Find loot stashes and special items with hand-drawn treasure maps.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fill out your bestiary to gain combat perks against different enemies.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Hunt for the hidden faeries and learn their wisdom.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Uncover and solve mysteries using your own perception and intuition.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Sail the seas to remote islands.</p></li></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402470/extras/b45ac0d087676f0c84ba23feb981262b.poster.avif?t=1764363478\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402470/extras/b45ac0d087676f0c84ba23feb981262b.webm?t=1764363478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402470/extras/b45ac0d087676f0c84ba23feb981262b.mp4?t=1764363478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402470/extras/5d419077064422b7c4a10ddd302eed40.avif?t=1764363478\" width=1200 height=278 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402470/extras/8328b68dacf9b1b2174c9c4c4eb61fa0.poster.avif?t=1764363478\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402470/extras/8328b68dacf9b1b2174c9c4c4eb61fa0.webm?t=1764363478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402470/extras/8328b68dacf9b1b2174c9c4c4eb61fa0.mp4?t=1764363478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The wonder of pixel art shines through the small unexpected details like the flapping of a butterfly's wings. From large animals to small critters you will find life in every corner of the world. There are over 10 unique realms in Anterra, each with their own flora and fauna, culture, lore and magical beasts to discover.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402470/extras/06b43b59f97fe67538a2339fc58bdfda.poster.avif?t=1764363478\" width=920 height=374 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402470/extras/06b43b59f97fe67538a2339fc58bdfda.webm?t=1764363478\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402470/extras/06b43b59f97fe67538a2339fc58bdfda.mp4?t=1764363478\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402470/extras/e0f2fa8c9ddcccf17cb1999c59b1e154.avif?t=1764363478\" width=1200 height=278 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >The interface design is focused on tactile items and icons rather than UIs, menus and text. Our item management systems are a great example of this. Move, equip, trade items, and drop them in the environment, all without opening a single menu.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >World of Anterra’s interface is integrated into the game using satisfying animations with in-world objects like bags and books. </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Dig through crates, chests and bags.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Flip through the pages in your spellbook and journal.</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Drag items freely from your backpack into the world.</p></li></ul>",
    "supported_languages": "英语<strong>*</strong>, 法语<strong>*</strong>, 意大利语<strong>*</strong>, 德语<strong>*</strong>, 西班牙语 - 西班牙<strong>*</strong>, 葡萄牙语 - 巴西<strong>*</strong>, 葡萄牙语 - 葡萄牙<strong>*</strong><br><strong>*</strong>具有完全音频支持的语言",
